<div id="use-of-data" class="tab ">
<div class="col-sm-12 terms-of-use">
<div class="information">
<div class="row">
<h4>7. Use of Data</h4>
<div class="col-sm-12">
<p>
<strong>7.1.</strong> We use information held about you in the following ways:
</p>
<ul class="indent-left">
<li>
<strong>7.1.1.</strong> To ensure that content from our site is presented in the most effective manner for you and for your computer;
</li>
<li>
<strong>7.1.2.</strong> To use it in data analytics and transfer to our operated systems for this purposes;
</li>
<li>
<strong>7.1.3.</strong> To provide you with information that you request from us or which we feel may interest you, where you have consented to be contacted for such purposes;
</li>
<li>
<strong>7.1.4.</strong> To conduct marketing analysis;
</li>
<li>
<strong>7.1.5.</strong> In the event that you are selected as "Learner of the Day" or "Learner of the Month", you agree to your details and responses being used in Alison marketing on Alison community pages; and
</li>
<li>
<strong>7.1.6.</strong> When a learner submits a testimonial or comment, they give permission for Alison to use that on the Alison website, community and in marketing material.
</li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>
